\cf0 Taught via 90 written lessons, code notebooks, videos, and instructor interaction - this is the perfect one-stop conversion course for software developers, machine learning engineers, data scientists, aspiring founder or computer science students to join the LLM revolution. In fact we think this is the most comprehensive LLM developer course out there. We will keep this course continuously updated and aim to make it the gold standard practical LLM developer certification.\
While the fundamental concepts can be grasped relatively quickly, becoming a proficient LLM developer involves cultivating a broader skillset than traditional software or machine learning roles often demand. This includes new non-technical and entrepreneurial skills that are key to this role such as learning to integrate industry expertise and make the right system design and product development decisions and economic trade-offs. It also includes more full-stack code and product understanding, communication and entrepreneurial skills. We teach the LLM developer technical skillset together with practical tips and new non-technical considerations that are key to the role. The course shares code and walks through the full process for building, iterating, and deploying a complex LLM project, the AI Tutor chatbot accompanying the course. To complete the course and receive certification, you will 
