\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 About Towards AI\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs24 \cf0 Towards AI has been teaching AI since 2019 and over 500,000 people have learned from our tutorials, articles and courses. In parallel, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://x.com/Whats_AI"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 Louis-Fran\'e7ois}} has also taught via {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.youtube.com/@whatsai"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 educational videos}} explaining research papers to millions of people. You may have also read our best-selling LLM book \'93Building LLMs for Production\'94 or taken our three-part GenAI:360 course series, which we released in partnership with Intel and Activeloop and reached over 40,000 students.\
Towards AI\'92s 15 AI engineers also deliver custom corporate AI training and LLM development consultancy; building AI engineering bootcamps for organisations such as Europol and developing production grade AI Workflows and Agents for corporates and stealth startups.\
All this is to say; we have been learning and actively applying the tricks of the LLM trade from day one; and in our courses we share our learnings and true practical tips rather than theory and flashy demos which don\'92t work in practice. We teach you lessons from both our successes and our failures of building AI systems that work in the real world. Our aim is that you won\'92t have to rediscover the same mistakes we found when developing these techniques for the first time!\
